<br>
Because of the server going down, we had a late start.  Doing FGs took some time.  Bamana and I worked on groups while this happened.  Then we started the buffing process.  This was the best buff line we've ever had.  Buffing went quick enough and was done completely.  We had a couple issues with buffs since we didn't have any Enchanters (had to import one just for the final Clarity/Speed buff) or Shamans.<br>
<br>
Where did we go wrong?  Two areas.  1)  Battle plan.  I called for waves and it didn't work out.  I know this appoach *can* work, but this wasn't the strategy needed for the run.  2)  The level of the participants.  We had several members at 40 and one Cleric at 38.  These folks tend to die rather quickly.<br>
<br>
I want to thank everyone who came out for Naggy.  We did manage to learn some things even though we didn't take him down.  I hope these lessons are beneficial to some of the other participants and raid leaders.<br>
<br>
At this time, I'm stepping down as a dragon raid leader for CoG.  I'm not going to be leading any dragon raids for a little bit.  I'll be happy to advise, but I recommend any other raid leaders take the time to research this undertaking.  If you need to contact me, please send me a tell or email (address found in the Members section of this site). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bcouncilofguilds.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=minkey>Minkey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(11/2/00 11:21:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> coming late</span><hr size=1> I came about 1 hour late and offered my services which I was informed wasnt needed. Im a 53 necro. When I contacted you, the FG slaughter had already begun. As a necro I can summon corpses and feed mana for the raid as well as assist physically in the FG hunt. I was disappointed that I wasnt allowed to come, im sure I couldve helped. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CBC6B1><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujzonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jzonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(11/2/00 11:40:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: coming late</span><hr size=1> I can understand your disappointment.  What I said was true.  We had more than enough people there to handle the FGs.  In fact, not everyone was fighting the FGs.<br>
<br>
Could you have helped?  Sure.  Feeding mana would have sped up the CR process just a touch.  As it was, we had three Bards feeding mana to the three ressing Clerics, plus Clarity from an Enchanter.<br>
<br>
We didn't need to summon any corpses in Naggy's lair this time.  Even so, we had the services of two Necros for this.<br>
<br>
This is just the way the raid worked out.  It happens. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=27.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=27.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=27.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.threadControl?topicID=27.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=27.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=27.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="councilofguildsgeneral">General<option value="councilofguildscouncildiscussions">Council Discussions<option value="councilofguildsevents">Events<option value="councilofguildscogplanesraidschedule">CoG Planes Raid Schedule<option va